search_results.lyrics:
Immortality LyricsI was only dreaming
A past encounter resurfacing
From deep violet water

I was only dreaming
A familiar gesture misplaced in time

I was only dreaming
Of something I left behind

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
"Things that accord in tone vibrate together
Things that have affinity in their inmost natures seek one another"

search_results.lyrics:
Slowness LyricsIn existential mathematics
The degree of slowness
Is directly proportional
To the intensity of memory

The degree of speed
Is directly proportional
To the intensity of forgetting

Why has the pleasure of slowness disappeared?You might also likeEmbed

description.plain:
Welcome to Christian Genius' July 2021 Singles Release Calendar!



For July 2021 album releases, visit this page



This page highlights all singles released in every genre of Christian music throughout 2021. Singles are listed with a hyperlinked title. Any songs that are not transcribed will have an indicated asterisk (*) next to the title.

How can you help?


Adding songs



If there’s a song you think should be listed on a specific calendar, add a comment at the bottom of the page.


Adding lyrics



If you transcribed a song, hyperlink the title.


Updating dates



If we have any dates wrong, etc, add a comment at the bottom of the page.
